Lil recap from my bday at Woodbooger ✨ 
thanks to everyone that said happy birthday and/or made me feel special. I really appreciate it 💜✨
There are many ups and downs with skating rn but I am happy I got to conquer this epic road and stay in one piece. 
It was so great to see the community come together again and to see so many familiar faces 🤗 
I’m looking forward to more adventures this summer ✨
